      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific will continue\nthe Sunday excursions to st. Maries.\nFerrell's and st. Joe during the sum\nmer. Train will leave Spokane 8 a.\nm. for Occur d'Alene. Steamer Cakes\nleaving there on arrival OF train for\nq delightful ride across the lake and\nUP the st. Joe river. arriving at Fer\nrell's about p. m. where stop Of\n80 minutes will be made for dinner.\nThose preferring to do 30 can take\nlunch baskets and eat lunch on tho\nboat. Returning train will arrive\nSpokane about y. m. Fare for the\nround trip 81."
    }
  ]
